Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.71,0:00:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天開始就是校外教學了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.72,0:00:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.44,0:00:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搞什麼呢 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說 好意外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嘴上說著麻煩 但還是參加了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.69,0:00:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也行啦 只要不學習就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.45,0:00:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為出席不夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.31,0:00:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然我們兩個是C組的 會找時間去看你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.00,0:00:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就和同樣是B組的白石同學好好相處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.68,0:00:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個 山田君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.56,0:00:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以過來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.44,0:00:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}麗 吃巧克力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:01:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是新品哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.22,0:01:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.04,0:01:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了 謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.06,0:01:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石那傢伙偶爾也能出出好主意嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.98,0:01:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣倒是好玩了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.52,0:01:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}麗 最近覺得你變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊是啊 以前你就知道學習都沒怎麼和你說話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.54,0:01:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且說山田到底是參加了我們組…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.18,0:01:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還說他不參加 就不去了什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.62,0:01:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那傢伙意外的也是有不錯的地方的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.92,0:01:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 山田吐了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8\fs35}討厭 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是暈車了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:21.72,title-blur,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur6\pos(640,600)\fad(300,0)}第四話「好像喜歡上山田君了」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:21.72,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,600)\fad(300,0)}第四話「好像喜歡上山田君了」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哦 今天要住在這兒了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比我想像中好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.06,0:03:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}麗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有山田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和A班的大家一起去散步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}聽到沒 你打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像還是很噁心 我在房間休息好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}麗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我馬上就來了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}應該更悠閒點兒的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼這麼快就到晚飯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這 這些傢伙是怪物麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}邊跑邊說話 到底是多有精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.50,0:04:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}麗 食堂在這邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們先去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請進
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼你在學習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我身體好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可是累得要死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}差不多該換回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能再等等嗎 我想把這本參考書再整理整理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.42,0:04:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}飽了飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石那傢伙 如果只想學習的話幹嘛來參加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}麗 我們帶點心來了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還要吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:05:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是 我肚子已經很飽了 再也吃不下了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對哦 接下來是要去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不在 跑哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼啦 就不要管山田了 我們去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是不快點去的話時間不夠了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}洗澡的順序是決定好的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}麗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:43.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真厲害 麗真是巨乳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也讓我摸摸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要 住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}累死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天晚上來臥談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}yeah！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還要繼續嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石還沒回來 真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就這麼睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.56,0:06:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是今天麗能來真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.24,0:06:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為這種活動你不是一直都沒參加嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是為什麼這一次卻來了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:25.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我們在嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛剛你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說居然又一個人在看書 而且參考書還增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你到底是為什麼來校外教學啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至今一直都沒有參加的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是這次卻參加了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是有什麼目的的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:07:01.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 我一直都想參加的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是到了這個節骨眼上 我卻不知道該怎麼和大家接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就交給山田君了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算是我也暈了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為那些傢伙接下來打算搞臥談誒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:19.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼我必須要配合她們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快回去吧 現在可不是說不知道的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.88,0:07:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說那傢伙明明這麼餓卻一直忍著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去食堂的話應該還能剩點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能過來一下嗎 山田君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我希望你能跟我來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}應該說初次見面吧 山田君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我叫小田切 寧寧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是學生會副會長哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自我介紹就算了 你到底找我幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.16,0:08:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}希望你能看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這不是我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在一個人都沒有的房間裡 你翻了白石的書包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開什麼玩笑 我怎麼會做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你還想裝糊塗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚飯之後 洗澡之前 白石不在房間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是那個時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她竟然用我的身體去自己的房間拿東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.28,0:08:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果這張照片讓全校都看見的話 會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.66,0:08:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會引起很大的轟動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.66,0:08:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想傳出去的話 就隨便好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為這是白石拜託我去做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎 那這個也是被拜託的咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然這張就解釋不了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過你要是答應我一個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就當作沒有拍過這些照片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}條件？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}後天的全國模擬考試
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你去阻止白石參加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.76,0:09:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要玩了 聽我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在聽呢 在聽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你知道那個女人到底在盤算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.48,0:09:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當然是拖我的後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成功讓白石同學決定升學 讓我加分不少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果白石不參加考試的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我校的綜合排名就會下降
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}導致學生會長對我的評價也會下降
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像麗的事情 無論好壞都會影響到宮村呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:10:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直說了吧 白石同學的缺席也填補不了小田切和我的差距
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那這次的模擬考試還是讓她缺席比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:08.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要小看那個女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你以為他會輕易地刪掉那些照片嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一旦讓她得逞一次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之後她還會不斷的要挾你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那樣的話 就讓白石幫我說明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就說內褲是我拜託山田君拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}內褲？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本來就是那傢伙做的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們那鄙視的眼神是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這麼一說白石同學也太可憐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}麗會變成一個讓山田幫自己那內褲的奇怪女生了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:44.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何等的恥辱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還偏偏是這個山田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是要刪掉照片 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.24,0:10:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要我和寧寧互換身體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.96,0:10:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不是知道的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.48,0:11:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵死了 你們也要替交換身體的我想一想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.32,0:11:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說回來 山田君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛剛趁亂抽到了鬼牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要以為能矇混過關
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底是什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}居然在這個時間叫我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.10,0:11:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且還是等著我從浴場出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是沒辦法的事吧 我怎麼知道你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你找我到底有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先說好 不接受關於白石麗的條件的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一切免談
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.94,0:11:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不是那麼無聊的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和我打個啵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說 和我打個啵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開什麼玩笑 為什麼要和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然對你沒有興趣 但還是答應你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先說好 之後發生什麼事我可不負責啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.26,0:12:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣就滿足了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 吻技爛死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰讓你自己擅自親上來…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奇怪…沒有交換…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奇怪了怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道那個女人有什麼特別的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道說 還有無法和你交換的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好吧 那我來確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}混蛋你胡搞些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的沒有交換…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:56.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的耶…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我試試
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看來只能是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你失去交換身體的能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是怎麼會突然失去能力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想得到的原因是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一定是累到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是發生很多事有點疲勞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不對 是交換身體時間太久了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太久？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總之今天太晚了 明天再試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.82,0:13:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把食材拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}醬汁還是鹽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}切 搞個烤肉有什麼意義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在外面吃味道又不會變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還是先和白石說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.04,0:13:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蕎麥面炒好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是炒麵…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.44,0:14:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小田切這樣說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好吧 模考不參加了 沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.84,0:14:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎麼能吃得下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是沒注意到 竟然被拍了照片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是說啊 為什麼你會盯著自己的內褲看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看入迷了而已 因為很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那種情形下？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且我的能力…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過 這樣也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多虧山田君 我的校外教學過得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}貼假睫毛的妙招 很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先進科技上都 日本人所展現出的靈巧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在假睫毛上也體現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}昨天一直在和大家聊天 受益匪淺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以現在都有點睏了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你說一直 是聊到早上？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}麗 回去了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.68,0:15:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}暑假…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}超研部的大家能一起去合宿就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快啊快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}超研部嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能力喪失的事情 還是先不要告訴她了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石沒參加模擬考 暫時阻止了照片外流
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以後怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.82,0:16:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那女人不一定就會乖乖刪掉照片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可惡 要是能和小田切交換身體就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.00,0:16:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早 早上好 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個山田…我為你…專門做了便當
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}討厭 太不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 宮村 這傢伙吃錯什麼藥了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其 其實我也給你準備了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:35.14,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H4F5252&\bord0\shad0\fs48\b1\pos(645,535)\fscx110}山田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}便當
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}卡通便當 做的還很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田要吃我的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼想都應該吃我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.28,0:16:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要吃誰的便當
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰的都不吃 我自己買了炒麵麵包的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}麻煩死了 你們倆到底想怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:56.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們倆…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像喜歡上山田你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什什什什 什麼情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再怎麼說也太突然了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是很突然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.02,0:17:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我們思考了一下 是從什麼時候開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後結論出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是在校外教學那晚和你接吻後 喜歡上你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是說 你不是失去了接吻和別人交換身體的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而是換成了接吻虜獲芳心的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虜獲芳心…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.40,0:17:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來 山田 香腸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說宮村 你給我滾邊上去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵死了 山田正吃我的飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們都給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說 為什麼要接吻啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這不是打回原形了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:18:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}煩人 你們就是知道會變回來才肆無忌憚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過還真是神奇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼山田突然看上去那麼帥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後這效果消失之後的失落 無力 沮喪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.70,0:18:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓人欲罷不能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們倆腦袋壞掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說回來山田 你得到了不得了的能力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.34,0:18:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣一來 學校裡的女生 不都是你的後宮了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7\fs35}\h\h山田時代來臨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才不稀罕這能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}少來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}害羞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田 你去試試吻白石嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}確實啊 被你搞定的麗會是什麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田君…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如君所願…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 這個可以有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好想吻一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}囉嗦 我怎麼可能做那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且我還沒告訴白石能力改變的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還沒說？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本來的確是想告訴她的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.24,0:19:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石同學是因為山田的交換能力進入超研部的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果沒了這個能力…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有的話 小麗就不會來超研部了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.72,0:19:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能和超研部的大家一起去合宿就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 這件事就瞞著白石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}趁此期間找回能力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:42.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原因和方法都還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原因嗎 除了和小田切吻過以外還能是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從那開始就變了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去找小田切 解決之前你們不要告訴白石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}炒麵包 和炒麵美的學校介紹環節
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.40,0:22:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們好 我是炒麵麵包精靈 炒麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.92,0:22:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家好 我是炒麵包的妹妹 炒麵美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.66,0:22:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天我們要造訪的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.20,0:22:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私立朱雀高等學校
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.64,0:22:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是一所一學年有1000人的超名門學校
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.68,0:22:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}優秀的學生有很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 作為名門重點校在當地很有名哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.36,0:22:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且還有著百年歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.64,0:22:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}保護著朱雀高中傳統的 是學生會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說是保護 不如說是支配
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.77,0:22:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的哥哥 這樣說不好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.82,0:22:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說的是實話 而且濫用權力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.28,0:23:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才沒有 那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.18,0:23:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有的吧 超火大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.12,0:23:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吃我這招
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:10.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.94,0:23:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}停 停
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.44,0:23:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們兩個 好好看劇本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.94,0:23:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.34,0:23:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然不該把學校介紹的視頻製作交給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.04,0:23:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你 你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.22,0:23:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}演的很好吧 我的炒麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的炒麵美也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.80,0:23:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}介紹學校怎麼能打起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.64,0:23:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣一來宮村同學和你們 評價肯定都降低了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.46,0:23:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}炒麵美…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.38,0:23:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.16,0:23:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7\fs35}\h\h等等 那預算也要被削減嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.11,0:23:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算是伊藤同學你也不能…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.82,0:23:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了 山田是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.68,0:23:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不對是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.86,0:23:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下集 山田君與七魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:23:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接吻可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.92,0:24:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當然 難得虜獲芳心的能力 要好好利用
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.52,0:24:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們真的會上癮的喲
