Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.67,0:02:06.60,optv-ch-sc-blur-v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)}{\blur4}如此不同的我們 應該不會錯過彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.39,0:02:14.40,optv-ch-sc-blur-v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)}{\blur4}對你說著 不要哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:18.02,optv-ch-sc-blur-v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)}{\blur4}秘密的約定 無法消失的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.23,0:02:21.15,optv-ch-sc-blur-v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)}{\blur4}若能說出 守護你 的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.15,0:02:23.49,optv-ch-sc-blur-v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)}{\blur4}一定會更輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:27.32,optv-ch-sc-blur-v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)}{\blur4}但是 已經沒有任何辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.53,0:02:29.79,optv-ch-sc-blur-v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)}{\blur4}再也無法離開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.95,0:02:34.87,optv-ch-sc-blur-v2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,100)}{\blur4}不想聽你的心裡話
